Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,====================AVANT====================
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.31,0:00:10.46,Default,,0,0,0,,剩下七隻
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.67,0:00:13.47,Default,,0,0,0,,這不是全體出動了嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.29,0:00:16.61,Default,,0,0,0,,總攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.06,0:00:19.12,Default,,0,0,0,,最糟糕的襲擊方式呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.08,0:00:21.35,Default,,0,0,0,,這一仗太有價值
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.35,0:00:22.87,Default,,0,0,0,,營養品都要增量了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.02,0:00:26.18,Default,,0,0,0,,樹也要嗑藥嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.41,0:00:28.44,Default,,0,0,0,,這個說法有點…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.58,0:00:32.28,Default,,0,0,0,,那邊為什麼不馬上攻過來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.60,0:00:33.32,Default,,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.75,0:00:38.38,Default,,0,0,0,,無論如何 既然不能去神樹大人庇護不到的牆外
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.87,0:00:41.01,Default,,0,0,0,,我們就沒法主動出擊呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.37,0:00:44.53,Default,,0,0,0,,敵人似乎會從緊貼牆壁的位置發動攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.20,0:00:46.08,Default,,0,0,0,,決戰了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.56,0:00:48.01,Default,,0,0,0,,大家也做好準備
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.76,0:00:55.63,Default,,0,0,0,,幹什麼啊 友奈
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.19,0:00:55.62,Back,,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,615)}咯吱咯吱咯吱
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.71,0:00:57.98,Default,,0,0,0,,不用緊張沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.27,0:00:59.41,Default,,0,0,0,,有大家在嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.50,0:01:04.28,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.89,0:01:08.31,Default,,0,0,0,,好 勇者部眾人變身
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.53,0:01:09.17,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.84,0:02:35.49,Default,,0,0,0,,敵人也是蠻拼的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.67,0:02:36.89,Default,,0,0,0,,反過來說
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.10,0:02:38.60,Default,,0,0,0,,只要殲滅這些傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.76,0:02:41.01,Default,,0,0,0,,戰鬥等於結束了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.22,0:02:44.62,Default,,0,0,0,,大家 這裡來做那個吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.84,0:02:46.85,Default,,0,0,0,,那個？ 哪個？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.06,0:02:52.50,Default,,0,0,0,,圓… 圓陣？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.56,0:02:53.64,Default,,0,0,0,,有必要嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.84,0:02:56.13,Default,,0,0,0,,決戰需要氣勢吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.34,0:02:58.12,Default,,0,0,0,,夏凜
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.65,0:03:01.94,Default,,0,0,0,,真是的 拿你們沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.49,0:03:04.36,Default,,0,0,0,,你們幾個
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.59,0:03:06.44,Default,,0,0,0,,贏了就請你們吃喜歡的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.58,0:03:08.13,Default,,0,0,0,,絕對不要死哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.37,0:03:11.45,Default,,0,0,0,,好 我要大吃特吃呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.54,0:03:13.02,Default,,0,0,0,,肉片蓋澆烏冬什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.13,0:03:15.12,Default,,0,0,0,,不用你說我也會殲滅它們
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.55,0:03:16.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我… 我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.37,0:03:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,因為我有想要實現的夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.49,0:03:22.94,Default,,0,0,0,,加油守護大家 守護國家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.64,0:03:27.87,Default,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.35,0:03:30.06,Default,,0,0,0,,勇者部fight
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.19,0:03:31.81,Default,,0,0,0,,喔！
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,====================Title====================
