Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,====================A-PART====================
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.51,0:05:07.65,Default,,0,0,0,,出陣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.83,0:05:11.41,Default,,0,0,0,,好 殲滅
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.50,0:05:12.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我們也是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.66,0:05:13.17,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.04,0:05:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,宿命點的前進速度各有不同
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.41,0:05:25.70,Default,,0,0,0,,那個巨大的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.37,0:05:28.22,Default,,0,0,0,,壓迫力明顯不同
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.48,0:05:30.39,Default,,0,0,0,,但首先是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.45,0:05:38.62,Default,,0,0,0,,頭功歸我啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.98,0:05:47.84,Default,,0,0,0,,首先是第一隻 封印掉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.05,0:05:51.54,Default,,0,0,0,,好厲害 夏凜！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.98,0:05:55.41,Default,,0,0,0,,其他敵人到達前 先打倒這傢伙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.92,0:06:03.46,Default,,0,0,0,,出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.70,0:06:07.45,Default,,0,0,0,,轉什麼轉！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.21,0:06:09.93,Default,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.80,0:06:13.05,Default,,0,0,0,,東鄉同學！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.36,0:06:23.11,Default,,0,0,0,,配合得漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.48,0:06:25.48,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝你 東鄉同學
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.90,0:06:31.68,Default,,0,0,0,,但是 剛才那敵人的舉動
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.60,0:06:35.32,Default,,0,0,0,,簡直是伸出臉來討打
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.29,0:06:37.84,Default,,0,0,0,,是陷阱？！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.94,0:06:46.28,Default,,0,0,0,,這個聲音怎麼回事 好難受
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.26,0:06:49.17,Default,,0,0,0,,這種程度 勇者的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.68,0:06:51.44,Default,,0,0,0,,大家！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.19,0:06:53.21,Default,,0,0,0,,是那個鈴鐺嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.52,0:07:02.56,Default,,0,0,0,,狙擊…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.42,0:07:06.54,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣下去的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.69,0:07:09.42,Default,,0,0,0,,不妙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.67,0:07:12.50,Default,,0,0,0,,聲音…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.09,0:07:16.22,Default,,0,0,0,,聲音是讓大家幸福的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.29,0:07:18.45,Default,,0,0,0,,這種聲音…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.13,0:07:23.94,Default,,0,0,0,,這種聲音！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.86,0:07:26.59,Default,,0,0,0,,樹！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.32,0:07:31.97,Default,,0,0,0,,首先是 你們倆！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.68,0:07:36.45,Default,,0,0,0,,姐姐！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.73,0:07:38.18,Default,,0,0,0,,真可靠
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.46,0:07:40.18,Default,,0,0,0,,好 三隻一起…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.92,0:07:41.46,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.68,0:07:42.57,Default,,0,0,0,,小樹！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.60,0:07:44.22,Default,,0,0,0,,樹 解開繩索
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.89,0:07:45.63,Default,,0,0,0,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.63,0:07:46.12,Default,,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.64,0:07:48.77,Default,,0,0,0,,情況不太對
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.01,0:07:52.97,Default,,0,0,0,,後退？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.89,0:08:15.85,Default,,0,0,0,,潛下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.60,0:08:17.89,Default,,0,0,0,,趁現在掩護
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.30,0:08:23.05,Default,,0,0,0,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.26,0:08:25.35,Default,,0,0,0,,合體了！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.65,0:08:26.39,Default,,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.49,0:08:28.20,Default,,0,0,0,,這種事我可沒聽說過啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.41,0:08:30.57,Default,,0,0,0,,但能一下打倒三隻哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.01,0:08:33.20,Default,,0,0,0,,友奈說的沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.75,0:08:35.35,Default,,0,0,0,,一併開始封印
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.36,0:08:44.16,Default,,0,0,0,,這玩意會跟蹤的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.47,0:08:45.08,Default,,0,0,0,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.33,0:08:53.99,Default,,0,0,0,,既然會追過來 就原物奉還
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.49,0:08:58.98,Default,,0,0,0,,快住手
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.28,0:09:04.01,Default,,0,0,0,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.51,0:09:06.15,Default,,0,0,0,,無效？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.46,0:09:15.49,Default,,0,0,0,,這…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.05,0:09:25.71,Default,,0,0,0,,神樹大人會…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.17,0:09:37.63,Default,,0,0,0,,不… 不是開玩笑的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.02,0:09:46.23,Default,,0,0,0,,姐姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.71,0:09:48.61,Default,,0,0,0,,不行 不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.36,0:09:52.55,Default,,0,0,0,,扔下樹 把大家捲進來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.14,0:09:55.05,Default,,0,0,0,,一個人早早掛掉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.59,0:09:58.85,Default,,0,0,0,,這怎麼行！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.51,0:10:22.95,Default,,0,0,0,,姐姐… 難道說…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.23,0:10:26.41,Default,,0,0,0,,解放積蓄的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.35,0:10:28.70,Default,,0,0,0,,勇者的殺手鐧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.44,0:10:31.98,Default,,0,0,0,,那就是… 滿開
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.10,0:10:44.76,Default,,0,0,0,,能行！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.97,0:10:56.86,Default,,0,0,0,,不可原諒
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.62,0:11:00.58,Default,,0,0,0,,東鄉同學 那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.38,0:11:01.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我方
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.11,0:11:08.69,Default,,0,0,0,,對敵軍實施總攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.55,0:11:18.93,Default,,0,0,0,,這種程度的敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.30,0:11:21.21,Default,,0,0,0,,看來都沒有封印的必要呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.74,0:11:30.62,Default,,0,0,0,,無論哪次都是這麼奇怪的死法
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.80,0:11:32.94,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.36,0:11:35.58,Default,,0,0,0,,離神樹大人好近
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.04,0:11:37.17,Default,,0,0,0,,這隻宿命點
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.05,0:11:39.52,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼沒注意到
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.50,0:11:45.55,Default,,0,0,0,,這傢伙 又小又快
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.32,0:11:52.64,Default,,0,0,0,,被輕易躲過了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.07,0:11:53.92,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣下去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.36,0:11:55.47,Default,,0,0,0,,神樹大人會…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.42,0:12:11.04,Default,,0,0,0,,休想破壞我們的日常
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.97,0:12:12.86,Default,,0,0,0,,小樹
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.32,0:12:13.91,Default,,0,0,0,,樹
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.56,0:12:18.22,Default,,0,0,0,,不許去那裡！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.12,0:12:28.14,Default,,0,0,0,,懲罰你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.35,0:12:44.05,Default,,0,0,0,,小樹 太好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.23,0:12:48.46,Default,,0,0,0,,可惡 我要躺到什麼時候啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.90,0:12:50.29,Default,,0,0,0,,樹 幹得好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.59,0:13:00.79,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼 這個看起來很難纏的有精神的球
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.88,0:13:03.67,Default,,0,0,0,,不好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.97,0:13:04.93,Default,,0,0,0,,姐姐！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.16,0:13:06.50,Default,,0,0,0,,勇者部全員
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.81,0:13:08.36,Default,,0,0,0,,封印開始！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.17,0:13:17.80,Default,,0,0,0,,趁我纏住這傢伙 快點！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.40,0:13:18.93,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.03,0:13:20.04,Default,,0,0,0,,知道啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.75,0:13:21.46,Default,,0,0,0,,收到
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.58,0:13:23.44,Default,,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.89,0:13:27.86,Default,,0,0,0,,也給我留下點甜頭啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.32,0:13:38.28,Default,,0,0,0,,好 不愧是勇者部
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.72,0:13:43.15,Default,,0,0,0,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.21,0:13:43.86,Default,,0,0,0,,風前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.86,0:13:44.76,Default,,0,0,0,,那傢伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.41,0:13:48.22,Default,,0,0,0,,打倒那傢伙！
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,====================B-PART====================
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.06,0:14:23.93,Default,,0,0,0,,無論哪方面 都太破天荒了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.40,0:14:27.18,Default,,0,0,0,,而且那個御靈 出現的地方是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.78,0:14:28.52,Default,,0,0,0,,宇宙？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.29,0:14:31.30,Default,,0,0,0,,大過頭了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.85,0:14:33.87,Default,,0,0,0,,那種東西 要怎麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.66,0:14:37.18,Default,,0,0,0,,最後的最後 居然這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.12,0:14:39.20,Default,,0,0,0,,該死
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.13,0:14:40.90,Default,,0,0,0,,沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.65,0:14:43.63,Default,,0,0,0,,因為是御靈
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.08,0:14:46.22,Default,,0,0,0,,只要像先前那樣對付就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.60,0:14:49.21,Default,,0,0,0,,無論敵人多麼巨大
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.58,0:14:50.70,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼能放棄呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.55,0:14:54.01,Default,,0,0,0,,所謂勇者 就是這樣的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.16,0:14:55.89,Default,,0,0,0,,友奈…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.28,0:14:57.10,Default,,0,0,0,,友奈
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.74,0:14:58.80,Default,,0,0,0,,友奈 走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.15,0:15:00.20,Default,,0,0,0,,現在的我的話
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.38,0:15:02.03,Default,,0,0,0,,應該能帶上友奈
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.35,0:15:04.97,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 封印就拜託你們兩個了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.37,0:15:07.30,Default,,0,0,0,,快點殲滅掉它哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.47,0:15:09.64,Default,,0,0,0,,友奈 東鄉前輩！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.89,0:15:38.93,Default,,0,0,0,,可惡 侵蝕好快
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.49,0:15:44.91,Default,,0,0,0,,拘束力要消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.37,0:16:03.69,Default,,0,0,0,,御靈會攻擊？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.96,0:16:04.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我們迎擊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.15,0:16:06.40,Default,,0,0,0,,不能讓它落到地上
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.64,0:16:17.45,Default,,0,0,0,,東鄉同學
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.93,0:16:20.44,Default,,0,0,0,,沒關係 友奈 看著吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.24,0:16:23.79,Default,,0,0,0,,一個也不會讓它通過的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.60,0:16:45.16,Default,,0,0,0,,好厲害 東鄉同學
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.44,0:16:46.68,Default,,0,0,0,,來到這裡了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.38,0:16:50.18,Default,,0,0,0,,東鄉同學
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.00,0:16:53.17,Default,,0,0,0,,友奈 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.06,0:16:55.73,Default,,0,0,0,,我似乎有點累了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.49,0:16:57.93,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝你 東鄉同學
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.69,0:17:01.88,Default,,0,0,0,,看著吧 我去幹掉它
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.63,0:17:08.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我會一直注視著你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.89,0:17:12.64,Default,,0,0,0,,滿開
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.70,0:17:35.88,Default,,0,0,0,,守護大家
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.31,0:17:41.65,Default,,0,0,0,,我要成為勇者！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.25,0:17:52.93,Default,,0,0,0,,就是那裡！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.05,0:18:00.02,Default,,0,0,0,,友奈…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.09,0:18:18.86,Default,,0,0,0,,好硬！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.50,0:18:27.03,Default,,0,0,0,,勇… 勇者部五條
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.52,0:18:33.01,Default,,0,0,0,,其一！ 盡量不放棄！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.80,0:18:36.92,Default,,0,0,0,,再來！ 五條！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.64,0:18:39.62,Default,,0,0,0,,又一條！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.36,0:18:45.97,Default,,0,0,0,,車到山前！ 多半！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.17,0:18:49.16,Default,,0,0,0,,有路！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.82,0:19:17.73,Default,,0,0,0,,成功啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.68,0:19:27.79,Default,,0,0,0,,東鄉同學
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.64,0:19:30.85,Default,,0,0,0,,友奈 辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.95,0:19:33.34,Default,,0,0,0,,風頭都被我…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.22,0:19:35.15,Default,,0,0,0,,搶去了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.65,0:19:38.30,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.25,0:19:42.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我用最後的力量 保住了這一點
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.04,0:19:45.04,Default,,0,0,0,,但不知能不能撐得住
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.86,0:19:46.80,Default,,0,0,0,,沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.17,0:19:50.41,Default,,0,0,0,,神樹大人會保佑我們的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.34,0:19:53.25,Default,,0,0,0,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.38,0:20:08.08,Default,,0,0,0,,就算萬一失敗了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.85,0:20:12.09,Default,,0,0,0,,有友奈在一起 我不怕
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.32,0:20:15.25,Default,,0,0,0,,神樹大人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.95,0:20:18.10,Default,,0,0,0,,請讓兩人平安歸來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.94,0:20:20.04,Default,,0,0,0,,拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.89,0:20:30.82,Default,,0,0,0,,好厲害的衝擊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.39,0:20:33.65,Default,,0,0,0,,絕對會救下她們的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.24,0:20:42.41,Default,,0,0,0,,堅持得不錯！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.57,0:20:44.05,Default,,0,0,0,,好厲害 樹 快看
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.31,0:20:45.66,Default,,0,0,0,,是你止住的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.85,0:20:46.58,Default,,0,0,0,,看
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.39,0:20:50.58,Default,,0,0,0,,去接她們吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.17,0:20:52.72,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.00,0:20:59.92,Default,,0,0,0,,姐姐 我… 努力了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.94,0:21:07.56,Default,,0,0,0,,營養品… 早知道就磕點了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.76,0:21:12.09,Default,,0,0,0,,友奈！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.26,0:21:13.83,Default,,0,0,0,,東鄉！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.41,0:21:16.20,Default,,0,0,0,,友奈 東鄉？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.62,0:21:19.81,Default,,0,0,0,,喂 你們振作點啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.06,0:21:34.94,Default,,0,0,0,,沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.20,0:21:44.80,Default,,0,0,0,,是… 姑且還活著
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.42,0:21:54.55,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼嘛 你們真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.65,0:21:59.18,Default,,0,0,0,,早點回話啦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.21,0:22:08.91,Default,,0,0,0,,不… 因為紅顏才薄命
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.91,0:22:11.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我這種總能化險為夷…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.51,0:22:13.47,Default,,0,0,0,,等等…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.81,0:22:16.26,Default,,0,0,0,,好癢 好癢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.57,0:22:19.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我是三好夏凜
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.21,0:22:22.92,Default,,0,0,0,,與宿命點交戰 負傷者4名
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.16,0:22:26.22,Default,,0,0,0,,希望馬上安排靈力醫療班
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.67,0:22:28.88,Default,,0,0,0,,另外 通過本次戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.00,0:22:30.52,Default,,0,0,0,,12隻宿命點
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.81,0:22:32.45,Default,,0,0,0,,全部被殲滅了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.10,0:22:36.53,Default,,0,0,0,,被我們贊州中學勇者部！
